{
  "texts": [
    "Thus, a QA system is tasked with learning to read and comprehend the clinical note provided a query and then extract information consisting of consecutive words from the notes relevant to the query from that note (Fig. 1).",
    "We use QA to address the information extraction problem for the following reasons.",
    "The texts in the clinical notes are very unstructured in nature.",
    "For example, the information regarding injection drug names can be presented in the notes in multiple forms, such as-opioids: denies recent use, hx ivdu, claims last use years ago.",
    "other drugs: hx methamphetamine use, has been using daily via injecting since a relapse in December; ivdu (cocaine/methamphetamine); reports using iv meth; iv cocaine mixed with heroine use; used meth by iv drug use; or history of daily heroine use, prior ivdu."
  ]
}